<refsection>
<title>Default</title>
    <cmdsynopsis>
        <command>g_vulnerableWeapons</command>
        <arg choice="plain"><literal>0</literal></arg>
    </cmdsynopsis>
</refsection>

<refsection>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
    <command>g_vulnerableWeapons</command>
    sets bitflags to enable missile-type weapons vulnerability.
    When enabled, the projectile (or equivalent) to become vulnerable to bullet fire or splash damage.
</para>
</refsection>

